reviewText:
The contents of the DVD (2 discs):

Universal Squadrons (2007)
Hellbinders (2009)
Fast Track: No Limits (2008)
Treasure Raiders (2007)
Distortion (2006)

Payback (2007)
Good Girl, Bad Girl (2006)
Mad Bad (2007)
Recon 2020: The Caprini Massacre (2004), (aka: Power Corps)
This Thing of Ours (2003)

Since these are not public domain movies, picture and sound qualities are quite good.  Reviews are uniformly mediocre; but purchase will be a matter of personal decision.
